{
  "text": "Primary canine myocardial cells from < 0.5 cm around the LSFPs were isolated from the control canine myocardium following the procedures described previously [CITATION_1] . Canine myocardial cells were maintained in Dulbecco's modified Eagle's medium (DMEM) supplemented with 10% fetal bovine serum and antibiotics (100 units/ml penicillin G and 100 units/ml streptomycin sulfate; Gibco, Grand Island, NY, USA).",
